name: ☠️ Unintended Consequences
description:
"☠️ Unintended Consequences" by BryantW

In the social sciences, unintended consequences (sometimes unanticipated consequences or unforeseen consequences) are outcomes of a purposeful action that are not intended or foreseen.

This artwork was created using old public domain illustrations collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in Photoshop.

5120px x 5120px .jpg - Date of completion 3/9/2022

About the artist - Bryant W. is a broken child born of the 80’s using his artistic skills to help the world find beauty within the ugliness that surrounds us all.
